Marines touched
down today in Norway, a move
designed to reassure

08:46.726 --> 08:52.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
nations nervous about Russia,
European officials
were digesting president-elect
Trump's latest

08:52.365 --> 08:54.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
comments about NATO.

08:54.601 --> 08:59.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
