the German
newspaper Bild that: "It's
obsolete because

08:59.372 --> 09:01.508 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
it wasn't taking care of terror.

09:01.541 --> 09:05.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the other thing is, the
countries aren't
paying their fair share, which I
think is

09:05.678 --> 09:08.248 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
very unfair to the United
States."

09:08.281 --> 09:13.620 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In fact, the only time the
alliance's mutual
defense provision was invoked
was to help

09:13.653 --> 09:17.424 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the United States after the 9/11
terror attacks.

09:17.457 --> 09:21.628 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Hundreds of NATO troops died
alongside Americans
in Afghanistan.

09:21.661 --> 09:26.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mr. Trump had made similar
statements during
the campaign, but this latest
barb came just

09:26.433 --> 09:31.237 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
