10:50.683 --> 10:53.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then we will see what sort of
cooperation
we can achieve.

10:53.520 --> 10:58.591 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Outgoing Secretary of
State John
Kerry went further in a CNN
interview.

10:58.625 --> 11:02.095 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: Well,
I thought, frankly, it was
inappropriate for

11:02.128 --> 11:06.232 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a president-elect of the United
States to
be stepping into the politics of
other countries

11:06.266 --> 11:08.134 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in a quite direct manner.

11:08.167 --> 11:12.338 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: The secretary said,
ultimately,
it's for Mr. Trump to explain
himself, because,

11:12.372 --> 11:17.443 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
