36:19.844 --> 36:24.916 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I asked her if she feels the
country has moved
past the kinds of racial
conflict that Forsyth

36:24.949 --> 36:25.917 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
experienced.

36:25.950 --> 36:27.986 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DEBBIE VERMAAT: No.

36:28.019 --> 36:33.758 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are still so many places
that are white
enclaves.

36:33.792 --> 36:36.261 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We are still a very segregated
country.

36:36.294 --> 36:40.999 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DUARTE GERALDINO: Confirming the
reasons Vermaat
was so fearful, the Southern
Poverty Law Center

36:41.032 --> 36:45.670 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
