racial intimidation since the
presidential

36:45.703 --> 36:47.172 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
election.

36:47.205 --> 36:57.148 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
Duarte Geraldino
in Forsyth County, Georgia.

36:57.182 --> 37:07.992 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In London
