37:25.243 --> 37:29.080 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
From London, special
correspondent Jennifer
Glasse reports.

37:29.114 --> 37:34.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNIFER GLASSE: The only thing
