private school are
not held to.

48:27.505 --> 48:31.342 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the for-profit's being
judged by the people
and whether or not they're
getting good jobs

48:31.375 --> 48:36.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
