course, with
the tuition at like a private
college is way

48:36.113 --> 48:38.616 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
more expensive than a for-profit
college.

48:38.649 --> 48:42.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
