49:14.185 --> 49:20.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the full statement from the
University
of Phoenix, go to the "PBS
NewsHour" Web site,

49:20.457 --> 49:22.226 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
