violated state law.

49:37.641 --> 49:43.581 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So far, the Department of
Education has approved
loan discharges of at least
28,000 former

49:43.614 --> 49:45.549 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
